# tests/ — Backend Test Suite
# format: ctx/1.0
# last-verified: 2026-03-26
# edges: -> call/render | ~> subscribe/read

## Master Suite
  test_suite : KG, NAI, persona, introspection, response, edge cases (50 tests) [test]
    ~> NAIService, PersonaService, IntrospectionService, ResponseService, JEWELRY_KG

## Adversarial / Security
  test_adversarial : 15 prompt-injection attacks against introspection engine [test]
    -> ADVERSARIAL_RESULTS
    ~> IntrospectionService
  ADVERSARIAL_RESULTS : Generated report: 15/15 attacks blocked [data]

## Game Pipeline
  test_game_interview : Question bank, depths, mirror bubbles, synthesis [test]
    ~> GameInterviewEngine
  test_game_generator : Synthesis to GameConfig: locations, NPCs, quests, items [test]
    ~> GameGenerator
  test_game_api : End-to-end: interview to gameplay integration [test]
    -> test_game_interview, test_game_generator, test_game_runtime
    ~> GameInterviewEngine, GameGenerator, GameRuntime
  test_game_runtime : Playable engine: nav, NPCs, quests, save/restore [test]
    -> test_game_generator
    ~> GameRuntime, GameGenerator
  test_gemini_integration : Live Gemini API: enrichment, dialogue, safety [test]
    ~> GeminiNarrative, TherapySafetyService, GameGenerator, GameInterviewEngine, GameRuntime

## Therapy Domain
  test_therapy_safety : 26 safety scenarios: crisis, blocks, guardrails [test]
    ~> TherapySafetyService
  test_therapy_kg : Per-user KG: CRUD, sessions, search, export [test]
    ~> TherapyKG
  test_therapy_personas : 4D persona computers: X, Y, Z, T dimensions [test]
    ~> TherapyEmotionalComputer, TherapyRelationalComputer, TherapyLinguisticComputer, TherapyTemporalComputer, TherapyKG
  test_therapy_service : Orchestrator pipeline: safety to KG to persona [test]
    ~> TherapyService
  test_therapist_dashboard : Clinical oversight: moods, flags, achievements [test]
    ~> TherapistDashboardService, TherapyKG

## Persona Stability
  test_persona_stability : 4D state consistency under manipulation [test]
    ~> PersonaService

## External Services
  IntrospectionService : Validates LLM output against 4D state [service]
  PersonaService : Computes 4D persona from user messages [service]
  NAIService : KG search and product retrieval [service]
  ResponseService : Full response pipeline orchestrator [service]
  GameInterviewEngine : Therapeutic game interview engine [service]
  GameGenerator : Synthesis to GameConfig [service]
  GameRuntime : Playable game engine [service]
  GeminiNarrative : Gemini API for narrative enrichment [service]
  TherapySafetyService : Crisis detection and safety blocks [service]
  TherapyService : Therapy session orchestrator [service]
  TherapistDashboardService : Clinical oversight dashboard [service]

## Persona Computers
  TherapyEmotionalComputer : X-axis: emotional state [service]
  TherapyRelationalComputer : Y-axis: KG relations [service]
  TherapyLinguisticComputer : Z-axis: voice/dialect [service]
  TherapyTemporalComputer : T-axis: session stages [service]

## Data Layer
  TherapyKG : Per-user SQLite KG [data]
  JEWELRY_KG : Jewelry store KG [data]
